{
  "name": "price-history",
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "description": "價歷追蹤器",
  "category": "U",
  "number": 402,
  "pain_point": "歷史價格追蹤",
  "commercial": "⚠️",
  "language": "Python",
  "dependencies": [
    "sqlite3",
    "click",
    "rich"
  ],
  "agent_compatible": true,
  "mcp_ready": true,
  "intent_triggers": [
    "這個商品的歷史價格走勢是什麼？",
    "幫我看一下這款產品過去幾個月的價格變化",
    "這東西之前有沒有比現在更便宜過？",
    "追蹤某商品的歷史售價紀錄",
    "我想知道這個型號最低曾經賣到多少錢",
    "幫我查一下上個月這個商品的價格",
    "現在這個價格是歷史低點嗎？"
  ],
  "examples": [
    {
      "query": "幫我查 Nike Air Max 90 過去 3 個月的價格紀錄",
      "params": {
        "product_name": "Nike Air Max 90",
        "days": 90
      }
    },
    {
      "query": "Switch 遊戲機最近半年的歷史價格走勢",
      "params": {
        "product_name": "Nintendo Switch OLED",
        "days": 180
      }
    },
    {
      "query": "這個商品的最低歷史成交價是多少？",
      "params": {
        "product_name": "Logitech MX Master 3",
        "days": 365
      }
    }
  ],
  "params_schema": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "days": {
        "type": "integer"
      },
      "product_name": {
        "type": "string"
      }
    },
    "required": [
      "days",
      "product_name"
    ]
  },
  "license": "MIT"
}
